---
title: Carb Smart Bacon and Chicken Breasts Taco Salad with Chipotle Crema and Charred Corn
description: This easy salad packs in flavour and a ton of protein from eggs, bacon, chicken and cheese. Lime and bacon fat are the base of this zesty dressing and we top it all off with a zippy chipotle sour cream drizzle.
